        "body": "<p>The <code>mainClassName<\/code> should consist out of the package and the class name itself, so in your case that should be:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>mainClassName = 'com.bachadiff.application.Application'\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>And since you are saying that you have a multi-project build, you should put this in the <code>build.gradle<\/code> for the <code>pictures-service-application<\/code> project<\/p>\n",
        "answer_id": 50480316,
        "question_id": 50477773
    }],
